.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-CAPACITY-MIN" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-capacity-min \- FEAT-2277 channel with smallest total capacity
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-capacity-min
.SH DESCRIPTION
channel-capacity-min for lightning CLI (FEAT-2277).
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN. Returns the channel whose local_msat plus remote_msat is smallest.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
